title: Playing Doctor
itunes:title: Playing Doctor
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Kate talks about adjusting to her new neighborhood, Leisha mentions playing doctor (for just a second) with a woman at a hike, and both learn the meaning of the non-word “fit”--- loving the clogs, by the way.
